snippet.title: DERELIKT Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit https://visuwyg.itch.io/derelikt for more information.
Follow development on twitter at https://twitter.com/kaffeebohnson

DERELIKT is a short narrative FPS inspired by Alien Resurrection (PS1, 2000) and Doom 3 (PC, 2004), with a dash of cosmic horror.
